## Annotation & Training Paths

CROAK supports two annotation workflows:

- **vfrog SSAT** — Auto-annotation via vfrog CLI. Upload images, run SSAT iterations, review in HALO. Train on vfrog's managed platform. Best for getting started quickly.
- **Classic** — Import annotations from external tools (CVAT, Label Studio, Roboflow) in YOLO/COCO/VOC format. Train on local GPU or Modal.com. Best for full control.

> `VFROG_API_KEY` is only needed for inference (`croak deploy vfrog`). Annotation and training use CLI authentication (`croak vfrog setup`).

